Changelog
=========

0.4.0 (2016-08-01)
------------------

Update to v0.4.0 of the Brotli library.

0.3.0 (2016-05-11)
------------------

Update to v0.3.0 of the Brotli library.

0.2.0 (2015-10-05)
------------------

Fix broken ``brotli.compress`` support on Windows.

0.1.3 (2015-10-05)
------------------

- Added basic for ``brotli.compress`` through a C wrapper included in this
  library.


